            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Delete_Permission_Set_Assignment</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Yes - Assigned</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <description>This flow automatically manages assignments to the Access Tickets AND Fields permission set. Users with active profiles of the types outlined below will be added to the permission set, while users who go inactive or moved to a different profile will be removed from the permission set. 

Profiles:
•	Carlyle Commercial
•	Compliance
•	Contracts
•	Credit
•	Executive
•	Finance
•	Lease Management
•	Legal
•	Technical User</description>
